---
title: Sheetpan Bibimbap-Inspired Beef and Veggie Bowls with Portabello Mushrooms and Sesame Eggs
description: Inspired by Korean bibimbap, this rice bowl has a it all, including savoury roasted vegetables and meaty mushrooms. There's a burst of flavour in every bite.
